name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Kylian Mbappe HD Wallpaper New Tab

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Dominate every new tab like Mbappé on the pitch! Customize shortcuts, use Google search, and enjoy exclusive football wallpapers.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Bring the electrifying energy of Kylian Mbappé to your browser with this new tab extension! A dynamic Google search bar makes your browsing as fast as Mbappé’s speed on the pitch. Access popular site shortcuts in a flash, or customize your own to match your style, just like he personalizes his game.

Every new tab features a fresh, action-packed football wallpaper, showcasing iconic moments from Mbappé’s career and more. With 10 updated backgrounds, each tab feels like stepping into the heart of the game.

Control your browsing experience the same way Mbappé controls the ball, with quick access to your favorite sites and changing visuals that keep things exciting. Whether you're watching highlights or keeping up with the latest news, this extension puts you in the mindset of a football star.

Channel the power and pace of Kylian Mbappé with each new tab and take your browsing game to the next level!
